summary: Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority, Inc.®Omega Omega ChapterPhiladelphia, Pennsylvania - The Omega Omega Chapter of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority, Inc.® has been serving the Philadelphia area since 1926. They focus on service, sisterhood, and community upliftment through various programs and events. The chapter celebrated 95 years of service in December 2021 under the leadership of International President Danette Anthony Reed.
